Class Cuadrado

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mp.sesion02.Figura

    public class Cuadrado
extends Rectangulo
    Heir Rectangle class. Able to create square objects. Square attributes making class inheritance rectangle (base and height) with the difference that in the case of a square side needs only one attribute; this nuance will treat the class constructor.
    Version:
    0.1 05/03/2015
    Author:
    Juan Antonio Rodríguez Baeza

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Cuadrado(double lado)
      The constructor of the class may define Square square from a single attribute side, making a call to the parent constructor (Rectangle), which passes the next attribute to construct a rectangle with base = height = side.
